          | :
        p
          code $color-form
          | Font color for the fields. (default:  $color-gray)
        p
          code $color-form-placeholder
          | Font color for the field-placeholder. (default: $color-gray-lighter)
        p
          code $color-background-form
          | Backgroudcolor for the fields. (default: $color-white)
        p
          code $color-border-form
          | Border color for the fields. (default: $color-gray)
        p
          code $color-background-form-focus
          | Background color for the fields, when they are focused. (default: lighten($color-brand-primary, 10%))
        p
          code $color-border-form-focus
          | Border color for the fields, when they are focused. (default: $color-brand-primary)
        p
          code $box-shadow-form
          | box shadow for the fields. (default: inset 0 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1)) 
